data.description: Beautiful 4 bed, 2 bath ranch home located  in Windsor Oaks West. Trusted lender Pat Miller (NMLS #698968) from Southern Trust mortgage (NMLS #2921) will provide a 1 % lender paid Buydown or .5% closing cost assistance on this listing.Conveniently located near Town Center, Mt. Trashmore & major interstates. New washer & dryer (2023). Home was majorly renovated in 2014-2015 including roof, vinyl, windows, HVAC, water heater, appliances. Well maintained & move-in ready.
